<ElliciumText Anchor="column#gutters" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2" class="rz-pt-12">
    Gutters
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    By default, the spacing between columns is set to <code>1rem</code>, via the <code>--rz-gap</code> CSS variable. Spacing between coulmns can be controlled by setting the <code>Gap</code> property of the parent <code>ElliciumRow</code> component.
</ElliciumText>
